Question 1: Find the mean, median, and standard deviation of the ratings for each of the movie genres. For each statistic
(mean, median, or standard deviation), only use a single MapReduce program.

Question 2: Using a single MapReduce program, identify the user who provides the most rating. Which genre does this user
watch the most?



